snippet.textDisplay:
Vestergaard 3/10

Vestergaard has been mostly awful for Southampton since he moved (saying this as a Saints fan) and has not even made the match day squad this season. He is surprisingly really bad in the air and gets caught out with the ball way too often for a top flight CB. When Saints went on their run of 6 wins in 8 games, he was nowhere near the starting line up and replaced with the much improved Jack Stephens. This will be Vestergaard’s last season at Southampton I think and expect him to be shipped out in the summer
